The note at the end doesn't tell us anything we haven't already learned (although it also doesn't make sense - SCP-3115/A hasn't been described, so how does the D Class know that the person in the video is /A?). And the note is also too casual -  - which is noticeable throughout the skip.

So much of this is cliché - I don't see the value here.







